you back from me all this time.

01:25:55.892 --> 01:25:58.217
- Thank you.
- You're welcome. Come on.

01:26:06.279 --> 01:26:07.358
Oh, man.

01:26:13.245 --> 01:26:16.697
Handle your business, baby. Handle it.

01:26:21.046 --> 01:26:22.920
Shelby, I have something...

01:26:23.007 --> 01:26:27.254
Julian, before you say anything, I just
want you to know that I forgive you.

01:26:27.553 --> 01:26:29.048
- You do?
- Yes.

01:26:29.138 --> 01:26:34.181
I know now that you were just succumbing
to that testosterone peer pressure.

01:26:35.104 --> 01:26:39.149
You wanted to be with me last night
and it ate you up that you couldn't.

01:26:39.442 --> 01:26:42.527
It just made sense that
you should continue to suffer...

01:26:42.613 --> 01:26:45.947
and think about the jeopardy
you put our relationship through...

01:26:46.033 --> 01:26:47.860
rather than let you have your way.

01:26:47.951 --> 01:26:49.612
- I have...
- We're out of time.

01:26:49.704 --> 01:26:51.993
I'm sure it can wait
until the reception.

01:26:52.082 --> 01:26:53.789
You better get inside.

01:26:57.964 --> 01:27:00.881
Candace! I'm so glad you could make it.

01:27:01.760 --> 01:27:04.168
You look great.

01:27:09.893 --> 01:27:11.637
Candace, this is Shelby.

01:27:12.188 --> 01:27:13.813
Shelby, Candace.

01:27:13.899 --> 01:27:16.473
