01:27:38.927 --> 01:27:41.881
Shelby, it's over.

01:27:42.682 --> 01:27:45.599
I am not the man for you.
And you are not the woman for me.

01:27:45.685 --> 01:27:47.974
So let's just stop fooling ourselves.

01:27:48.063 --> 01:27:52.227
I hope you find what you're looking for,
because that's what I plan to do.

01:27:54.403 --> 01:27:57.025
I have to go. 'Bye, Shelby.

01:28:03.873 --> 01:28:05.996
Don't you think you oughta pick that up?

01:28:06.084 --> 01:28:07.162
What?

01:28:07.502 --> 01:28:08.913
Your bottom jaw.

01:28:09.880 --> 01:28:12.501
Q. 'Morning, Shelby.

01:28:12.799 --> 01:28:15.884
- Go to hell!
- I'll probably see you there.

01:28:18.013 --> 01:28:19.556
Where's Lance?

01:28:19.683 --> 01:28:22.173
I was just gonna ask you the same thing.

01:28:23.061 --> 01:28:26.348
- I'm sorry. Robin, Quentin.
- How you doin'?

01:28:26.607 --> 01:28:27.686
Hi.

01:28:29.109 --> 01:28:32.028
- Hi. You must be Robin.
- Hi. My pleasure.

01:28:32.197 --> 01:28:33.442
This is Murch.

01:28:33.656 --> 01:28:36.326
- This idiot don't know where Lance is.
- What?

01:28:37.495 --> 01:28:40.449
That's not good. Not good at all.
What are we gonna do?

01:28:40.540 --> 01:28:41.619
- I don't know.
- Something?

01:28:41.707 --> 01:28:42.823
You're not helping.

01:28:42.918 --> 01:28:46.287
- You need to figure something out.
- I'm under stress here.

01:28:49.174 --> 01:28:51.582
It's your fault that all this happened.

01:28:53.096 --> 01:28:54.839
What have you been doin'?

01:28:55.974 --> 01:28:58.596
Lance. Lance! Hey!

01:28:59.436 --> 01:29:03.102
I told you the wedding is off.
I came to tell my parents that I'm out.

01:29:03.191 --> 01:29:06.525
