01:29:27.844 --> 01:29:31.130
I don't know. Divine intervention.
I don't know!

01:29:31.306 --> 01:29:33.383
Just get in there. Be creative.

01:29:35.102 --> 01:29:38.638
- Divine intervention.
- Hey, you can do this.

01:29:39.775 --> 01:29:41.234
You have to.

01:29:42.319 --> 01:29:43.350
Go.

01:29:50.954 --> 01:29:55.451
Don't do this. You don't wanna do this.
You just need to breathe, relax.

01:29:55.709 --> 01:29:58.082
- Lance, hold on, man.
- Will you hold up?

01:29:58.171 --> 01:29:59.749
Please don't do this.

01:30:03.218 --> 01:30:05.591
Mama, Daddy, I got something
I gotta tell you.

01:30:05.679 --> 01:30:09.464
Wait! Lance, wait.
I gotta tell you somethin'.

01:30:12.228 --> 01:30:14.387
Lance! Pray!

01:30:14.898 --> 01:30:16.310
Wait for a second.

01:30:18.777 --> 01:30:20.107
What'd you say?

01:30:22.031 --> 01:30:23.656
Pray. Pray.

01:30:24.576 --> 01:30:26.984
You want me to beat you
down again, man?

01:30:37.257 --> 01:30:38.835
