01:34:17.010 --> 01:34:21.174
I could've killed you last night.
You know that? I still could right now.

01:34:22.141 --> 01:34:25.676
You could, man,
but it wouldn't change anything.

01:34:27.814 --> 01:34:31.231
I made a terrible, terrible mistake.

01:34:33.070 --> 01:34:34.529
And I'm sorry, man.

01:34:36.699 --> 01:34:39.321
- I would give you my right arm...
- Fuck that.

01:34:46.252 --> 01:34:49.206
