- You're not being realistic.

01:34:53.344 --> 01:34:56.215
This isn't the Bible.
This is the real world.

01:34:56.555 --> 01:35:00.803
And Mia is as close to perfection
as you're gonna get.

01:35:01.019 --> 01:35:04.851
I guess you got all the answers.
Everything is so fucking logical to you.

01:35:04.940 --> 01:35:06.518
Come on. You're in a church.

01:35:06.609 --> 01:35:09.943
The answers are fucked wherever you are!
You can't control me.

01:35:10.029 --> 01:35:14.110
I'm not one of your little characters
in one of your little stories, man!

01:35:14.451 --> 01:35:18.449
You can't control this outcome.
You know why? Because you are not God.

01:35:19.498 --> 01:35:22.535
- That's reality, motherfucker!
- Listen to reason.

01:35:37.937 --> 01:35:39.311
I knew.

01:35:41.815 --> 01:35:45.979
I always knew in the back of my mind
that she had been with somebody else.

01:35:46.196 --> 01:35:49.067
But never in a million lifetimes
would I think...

01:35:50.325 --> 01:35:54.075
