I have to like it.

01:37:08.749 --> 01:37:09.781
Okay.

01:37:10.251 --> 01:37:13.252
You better find a way to deal
with your issues, too.

01:37:13.337 --> 01:37:15.586
Writing is not gonna
purge you completely,

01:37:15.587 --> 01:37:17.835
so I suggest that you acknowledge Him.

01:37:19.387 --> 01:37:20.418
Him who?

01:37:24.768 --> 01:37:26.178
Okay.

01:37:30.608 --> 01:37:33.692
I feel you, but if I don't get you
into this tux...

01:37:37.241 --> 01:37:39.992
You said you'd get me over that broom.
Remember?

01:37:40.077 --> 01:37:42.366
- I remember.
- Then don't back out on me.

01:37:42.455 --> 01:37:45.207
You recognize His strength.
You respect it.

01:37:47.919 --> 01:37:50.292
Recognize. Respect.

01:37:50.964 --> 01:37:52.044
Okay.

01:39:45.805 --> 01:39:50.800
"Dearly beloved, we are gathered
here today in the sight of God...

01:39:51.686 --> 01:39:55.436
"...to join this man and this woman
in holy matrimony."

01:39:57.985 --> 01:40:00.442
The couple have written
their own wedding vows...

01:40:00.530 --> 01:40:03.531
that they'll speak to each other,
and in front of you...

01:40:03.617 --> 01:40:05.740
their family and dear friends.

01:40:09.457 --> 01:40:10.620
Mia?

01:40:18.091 --> 01:40:20.464
"Lance, my friend...

01:40:22.264 --> 01:40:24.470
"...my love, my hero...

01:40:29.146 --> 01:40:31.139
"...loving you is my heart's joy.

01:40:32.400 --> 01:40:35.900
"It teaches me to be faithful
to my personal truths.

01:40:38.407 --> 01:40:40.614
"As I stand beside you this day...

01:40:41.369 --> 01:40:43.943
"...I offer you the very heart of me...

01:40:45.874 --> 01:40:48.543
"...filled with sacred love...

01:40:49.252 --> 01:40:53.500
"...pure, unconditional and everlasting.

01:40:54.717 --> 01:40:56.876
"For love bears all things...

01:40:57.554 --> 01:41:01.386
"...endures all things
and believes all things.

01:41:01.976 --> 01:41:03.684
"Love never fails.

01:41:05.063 --> 01:41:06.972
"And I do love you, Lance...

01:41:08.608 --> 01:41:10.518
"...mind, body and soul."

01:41:22.415 --> 01:41:23.411
"Mia...

01:41:24.418 --> 01:41:26.957
"...my darling, my love...

01:41:29.132 --> 01:41:31.290
"...as I stand beside you this day...

01:41:32.094 --> 01:41:34.965
"...know that there is nothing greater
than love.

01:41:35.806 --> 01:41:37.431
"For God is love.

01:41:39.810 --> 01:41:42.100
"And having faith in you...

01:41:44.983 --> 01:41:46.940
"...and belief in our love...

01:41:49.780 --> 01:41:51.690
"...makes life worth living.

01:41:52.909 --> 01:41:54.452
"And as I stare...

01:42:02.545 --> 01:42:06.591
"As I stare upon your angelic face...

01:42:11.263 --> 01:42:15.392
"...I am made whole today,
a man with a higher purpose.

01:42:16.186 --> 01:42:19.804
"For a woman's virtue
is a man's greatest glory.

01:42:22.318 --> 01:42:24.026
"From this day forth...

01:42:24.695 --> 01:42:28.564
"...we should love one another
as God loves us."

01:42:32.997 --> 01:42:34.540
The rings, please.

01:42:38.920 --> 01:42:42.455
"By the power vested in me,
I now pronounce you...

01:42:42.925 --> 01:42:44.633
"...husband and wife."

01:42:46.345 --> 01:42:48.173
Please, kiss your bride.

01:43:49.668 --> 01:43:52.338
Mia gave me too much credit
for this union.

01:43:53.839 --> 01:43:55.916
I have learned from them...

01:43:57.678 --> 01:44:01.546
what it means to be truly committed
to another person.

01:44:03.017 --> 01:44:05.639
I have learned the importance...

01:44:06.604 --> 01:44:08.348
of seizing the moment.

01:44:09.775 --> 01:44:11.602
Because you can't go back.

01:44:13.321 --> 01:44:16.192
You can never go back.
You have to live for today.

01:44:17.533 --> 01:44:22.529
Not for what was, or could have been.

01:44:25.043 --> 01:44:26.537
And what will be...

01:44:28.546 --> 01:44:30.255
no one can say.

01:44:34.928 --> 01:44:36.258
But sometimes...

01:44:40.101 --> 01:44:42.509
you just have to step out on faith.

01:44:45.357 --> 01:44:46.935
And believe that...

01:44:47.360 --> 01:44:51.488
what you have built together
is worth preserving.

01:44:55.870 --> 01:44:58.954
Because when you're made
for each other as much...

01:45:01.125 --> 01:45:02.834
as these two are...

01:45:06.757 --> 01:45:08.335
it's definitely...

01:45:09.677 --> 01:45:11.717
definitely worth preserving.

01:45:22.234 --> 01:45:24.060
So, to the bride and groom.

01:45:27.364 --> 01:45:28.775
Lance and Mia...

01:45:29.659 --> 01:45:30.987
I love you.

01:45:33.246 --> 01:45:35.998
And may God bless this union.

01:45:40.629 --> 01:45:41.709
Cheers.

01:46:02.321 --> 01:46:03.484
Bravo, baby.

01:46:35.943 --> 01:46:38.648
Okay, ladies, who's ready
to catch the bouquet?

01:46:38.738 --> 01:46:41.312
Single females, on the floor. Let's go.

01:46:41.408 --> 01:46:43.365
Mia, are you ready?

01:46:44.995 --> 01:46:46.656
Okay, here we go.

01:46:52.963 --> 01:46:53.912
Bitch.

01:46:54.172 --> 01:46:55.371
Thanks, Mia.

01:46:58.302 --> 01:47:01.637
- All right. You know what comes next.
- Go get your girl.

01:47:01.722 --> 01:47:03.217
Come on out, y'all.

01:47:03.767 --> 01:47:06.055
- Q, you know you want to.
- What?

01:47:06.144 --> 01:47:09.311
Uncle Skeeter, you don't need
to catch this. Sit your butt down.

01:47:09.398 --> 01:47:12.435
Let's see what happens.
Just throw. You never know.

01:47:16.573 --> 01:47:17.653
I did not!

01:47:25.416 --> 01:47:26.911
I'm gettin' you.

01:48:00.832 --> 01:48:02.078
Cut it out.

01:48:02.168 --> 01:48:04.373
Quit acting like you don't like it.

01:48:08.716 --> 01:48:09.914
You like it.

01:48:13.972 --> 01:48:15.550
Say you like it.

01:48:19.938 --> 01:48:21.266
Say you like it.

01:48:22.858 --> 01:48:24.186
Stop it!

01:48:27.321 --> 01:48:29.231
Don't let her get away, dog.

01:48:35.622 --> 01:48:37.200
- Go get her, Q.
- That's scary.

01:48:39.084 --> 01:48:41.001
I think we have to dance.
Care to dance?

01:48:41.002 --> 01:48:42.917
Yes, I'd love to.

01:48:47.720 --> 01:48:51.255
Quentin better be careful
before Shelby puts a hurtin' on him.

01:48:53.184 --> 01:48:54.216
Yeah.

01:48:57.356 --> 01:48:58.980
Dance with me?

01:49:00.150 --> 01:49:01.395
You know...

01:49:03.071 --> 01:49:05.644
I just want to talk to you.

01:49:15.126 --> 01:49:17.285
Cut a rug with a war vet, darling?

01:49:18.839 --> 01:49:20.796
Sure, Uncle Skeeter.

01:49:21.007 --> 01:49:22.171
Come on.

01:49:28.475 --> 01:49:31.761
It's been a crazy-ass,
emotional weekend, hasn't it?

01:49:32.646 --> 01:49:35.103
Damn roller-coaster ride.

01:49:38.194 --> 01:49:40.864
Listen, about last night, Jordan.

01:49:41.990 --> 01:49:45.740
I don't want to hear about last night.
If I hear you mention last night...

01:49:45.827 --> 01:49:49.577
I'm gonna call the Enquirer
and tell them everything I know.

01:49:49.833 --> 01:49:51.457
So it's like that?

01:49:51.752 --> 01:49:55.833
Okay, I hear you loud and clear,
Miss Armstrong. Thank you.

01:49:56.924 --> 01:49:58.253
You're welcome.

01:50:06.477 --> 01:50:08.803
I saw you grabbin' for that garter.

01:50:13.193 --> 01:50:14.652
You know what?

01:50:15.695 --> 01:50:17.190
I don't blame you.

01:50:18.241 --> 01:50:20.067
She's a beautiful woman.

01:50:20.868 --> 01:50:22.493
She's the one.

01:50:25.541 --> 01:50:27.082
Just don't blow it.

01:50:34.426 --> 01:50:36.134
I love you, Harper.

01:50:50.653 --> 01:50:53.061
Excuse me, Robin,
I don't mean to interrupt...

01:50:53.155 --> 01:50:55.528
but Uncle Skeeter
did promise me a dance.

01:50:55.617 --> 01:50:59.829
Seeing he's the only available man in
the whole wedding party, I was just...

01:50:59.913 --> 01:51:02.749
Come on, baby girl.
You don't mind, do you, darling?

01:51:02.833 --> 01:51:04.458
No, not at all.

01:51:05.962 --> 01:51:09.248
And besides I think the best man
over there needs you.

01:51:17.392 --> 01:51:20.309
Come on, Uncle Skeeter.
Don't be tryin' to touch my booty.

01:51:20.395 --> 01:51:21.558
No, no.

01:51:43.130 --> 01:51:45.538
Thank you for helping me today.

01:51:47.593 --> 01:51:48.874
You're welcome.

01:51:50.555 --> 01:51:51.883
Great speech.

01:51:55.519 --> 01:51:58.189
- I was moved.
- You know I meant every word...

01:51:58.940 --> 01:52:01.811
every word I said about
preserving what we have, and...

01:52:01.901 --> 01:52:04.571
I don't think that this
is the right time.

01:52:06.156 --> 01:52:09.941
We have a lot to talk about
and it's not gonna be solved overnight.

01:52:11.036 --> 01:52:14.536
- We have to figure out some...
- You know what your problem is?

01:52:15.250 --> 01:52:17.326
You don't live enough for today.

01:52:18.628 --> 01:52:19.874
What?

01:52:21.799 --> 01:52:23.958
For once, just live in the moment.

01:52:30.226 --> 01:52:31.886
Harper, what are you doing?

01:52:31.978 --> 01:52:33.887
At least for a little while.

01:52:42.364 --> 01:52:43.444
Robin...

01:52:47.829 --> 01:52:49.407
will you marry me?

01:52:53.544 --> 01:52:55.002
I love you.

01:52:59.717 --> 01:53:00.832
Please.

01:53:05.767 --> 01:53:06.798
Yeah.

01:53:09.312 --> 01:53:10.640
Whatever, man.

01:54:20.018 --> 01:54:22.094
Come and get it goin' on, y'all.

01:54:22.271 --> 01:54:24.560
Five, six, seven, eight.

01:56:14.650 --> 01:56:16.025
Housekeeping.

01:56:26.747 --> 01:56:29.155
- Damn! I shouldn't have drank!
- What did I do?

01:56:29.250 --> 01:56:32.002
I ain't drinkin' no more liquor!

01:56:33.672 --> 01:56:35.380
Did you touch me?

